     <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">Introduction</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/description\">description</a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/manifest_version\">manifest_version</a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/name\">name</a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/version\">version</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n     <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Extension Workshop</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/\">Develop</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/publish/\">Publish</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/manage/\">Manage</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/enterprise/\">Enterprise</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Contact_us\"><strong>Contact us</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Channels</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.mozilla.org/addons\">Add-ons blog</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://discourse.mozilla.org/c/add-ons\">Add-ons forum</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://chat.mozilla.org/#/room/%23addons:mozilla.org\">Add-ons chat</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<table class=\"fullwidth-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 30%;\">Typ</th>\n   <td><code>String (ciąg znaków)</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Obowiązkowe</th>\n   <td>Tak</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Przykład</th>\n   <td>\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0.1\"</span></code></pre></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Wersja rozszerzenia, sformatowana jako liczby i znaki&nbsp;ASCII oddzielone kropkami. Szczegółowe informacje na temat formatu wersji znajdują się na stronie&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Toolkit_version_format\">Format Wersji</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Pamiętaj, że&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/manifest/version\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">składnia zdefiniowana dla&nbsp;<code>version</code> w Chromie</a>&nbsp;jest&nbsp;bardziej restrykcyjna niż ta&nbsp;używana w &nbsp;przeglądarce Firefox:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>wartości&nbsp;<code>version</code>&nbsp;ważne w&nbsp;Chrome zawsze będą ważne w&nbsp;Firefox</li>\n <li>wartości&nbsp;<code>version</code>&nbsp;ważne w&nbsp;Firefox mogą nie być ważne w&nbsp;Chrome</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0.1\"</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Zgodność z przeglądarkami","id":"zgodność_z_przeglądarkami","isH3":false,"query":"webextensions.manifest.version","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/version/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Przykład","id":"przykład"},{"text":"Zgodność z przeglądarkami","id":"zgodność_z_przeglądarkami"}],"summary":"Wersja rozszerzenia, sformatowana jako liczby i znaki ASCII oddzielone kropkami. Szczegółowe informacje na temat formatu wersji znajdują się na stronie Format Wersji.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"version","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"version","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"version","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"ключ version","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"version","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/manifest.json/version","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/manifest.json/version/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"Dodatki"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"Browser extensions"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json","title":"manifest.json"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/version","title":"version"}],"pageTitle":"version - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}